   Dating Infidelity Scale (PDIS) to assess attitudes toward specific
   behaviors that constitute these types of infidelity in romantic
   relationships. Exploratory and confirmatory factor analyses indicated
   three factors to the scale: Ambiguous, Deceptive, and Explicit
