Abstract = {Drawing on the mood regulation and job-stress recovery literature, four
   self-report measures for assessing how individuals unwind and recuperate
   from work during leisure time were developed (Study 1). Confirmatory
   factor analyses with a calibration and a cross-validation sample (total
   N = 930) showed that four recovery experiences can be differentiated:
