Abstract = {Psychometric review of 33 peer-reviewed studies of six self-report
   emotional intelligence (EI) measures supports a multidimensional
   conceptualization, of EI. The nature and number of EI facets, however,
   and their distinctiveness from more established trait domains is
   unclear. Building on earlier efforts, three studies were undertaken (Ns
   = 138, 163, 152) to develop self-report measures of 10 facets of EI
