   luxury brand aspiration were identified through prior literature review
   and qualitative investigations. This was followed by a series of scale
   development studies suggested by Churchill ( 1979).
   Findings - The results supported that the second-order measure of
   consumer's luxury brand aspiration consist of four related first-order
