   factor analysis, and validation through the use of confirmatory factor
   analysis and structural equation modeling.
   Findings - The paper conceptualizes and validates the concept of
   customer/service experience. In total, 19 items in four dimensions of
   the EXQ scale were identified: product experience, outcome focus,
   moments-of-truth and peace-of-mind. These dimensions reflect service
   experience perceptions. The findings support the conclusion that the
